  "detailed_description": "<h1>AWARDS</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/27f584a59d114ea49e2de76b7b72f2ff.avif?t=1766332152\" width=600 height=82 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Dreamlike Noir Where the Story is the Key</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📌 <i>Oniria Crimes</i> is an <strong>interactive noir novel with point & click mechanics</strong>. Explore crime scenes in a dreamlike world where objects are the only witnesses. <strong>Inspect every detail, uncover clues, and decide the fate of each suspect.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/6de80e3f7bd496f1f38853cad3e3508a.poster.avif?t=1766332152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/6de80e3f7bd496f1f38853cad3e3508a.webm?t=1766332152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/6de80e3f7bd496f1f38853cad3e3508a.mp4?t=1766332152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔎 <strong>Six cases, six crimes… and a secret that binds them together.</strong> What seems like a series of isolated investigations is actually part of a much bigger mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 <strong>Immerse yourself in a unique noir atmosphere</strong>, featuring an engaging narrative, sharp dialogues, and a world full of secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚠️ This is not an action game nor an open-ended deduction experience, but <strong>an interactive story driven by narrative exploration.</strong> If you enjoy mystery novels with a strong investigative component, <i>Oniria Crimes</i> will draw you in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you dare to uncover the crimes of Oniria?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/a9048b160e896f23f0b38601dab0fb75.poster.avif?t=1766332152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/a9048b160e896f23f0b38601dab0fb75.webm?t=1766332152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/a9048b160e896f23f0b38601dab0fb75.mp4?t=1766332152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
